trans-unit.source: Specifies where a chart element, such as a legend or title, will be docked on the chart.
trans-unit.target: Anger om ett diagramelement, till exempel en förklaring eller titeln, dockas på diagrammet.

trans-unit.source: The Docking enumeration represents the docking location on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart> control that an chart element should be docked.
trans-unit.target: Dockning uppräkningen representerar docka platsen på den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>Kontrollera att ett diagramelement bör vara dockad.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.Chart>

trans-unit.source: Set the `IsDockedInsideChartArea` property of the relevant chart element to specify whether that element will be docked to the entire chart image or to a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea>object.
trans-unit.target: Ange den `IsDockedInsideChartArea` -egenskapen för det relevanta diagramelementet att ange om elementet dockad hela diagrammet eller till en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea>objektet.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea>

trans-unit.source: The chart area is specified in the [DockedToChartArea](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) property of the chart element.
trans-unit.target: Diagramområdet som anges i den [DockedToChartArea](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) -egenskapen för diagramelementet.

trans-unit.source: Docked to the bottom of either the chart image or a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Dockad längst ned i antingen diagrambilden eller en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: Docked to the left of either the chart image or a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Dockad till vänster om antingen diagrambilden eller en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: Docked to the right of either the chart image or a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Dockad till höger om antingen diagrambilden eller en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"> </xref> objekt.

trans-unit.source: Docked to the top of either the chart image or a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Dockad längst upp i antingen diagrambilden eller en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataVisualization.Charting.ChartArea"> </xref> objekt.
